metadata.title: Tissot Men's T0554301104700 PRC 200 Analog Display Swiss Automatic Silver-Tone Watch
features: Round watch with blue dial, day/date window at 3 o'clock, silver-tone indexes and Arabic numerals, and stationary bezel
39 mm stainless steel case with anti-reflective sapphire dial window
Swiss automatic movement with analog display
Stainless steel five-link bracelet with deployant closure
Water resistant to 200 m (660 ft): In general, suitable for professional marine activity and serious surface water sports, but not scuba diving
description: Stainless steel case with a stainless steel bracelet. Fixed stainless steel bezel. Blue dial with silver-tone hands and index hour markers. Arabic numerals mark the 6, 9 and 12 o'clock positions.
